\frac{1+\cos x}{1-\cos x}=\frac1{(\csc x-\cot x)^2}=\frac{(\csc x+\cot x)^2}{(\csc^2x-\cot^2x)^2}=
(\csc x+\cot x)^2=\frac1{\tan^2x}+\frac2{\tan x\sin x}+\frac1{\sin^2x}
